                    "text": "  - with seabios bios.bin we get a lot of messages saying \"BUG: kvm_dirty_pages_log_enable_slot: invalid parameters\".\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "  - with vgabios.bin and -vga std we get 800x600x4 maximum resolution, as a fallback in qemu.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I have tested different combinations of bios.bin and vgabios.bin, supplied by seabios and vgabios vs supplied by qemu sources, and have determined the two problems are completely independent.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "  In fact, you get full vga resolution with seabios bios.bin and the qemu source's vgabios.bin, however the kvm_dirty_pages do appear.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
